{"tid":1883384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國強調停課不停學 確保學生能網上學習 現實執行係裝‘無限寶’軟件全面監控","createTime":"2020-02-17T02:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T02:20:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67644dc709382acf4e2baed6a0a2c731abf6fef6","tid":1883384,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"教育局早前宣佈將中小學復課日期進一步延期至 3 月 16 日或以後，不少學校已經推出相應措施，例如老師網上直播或錄影授課，又會通過網絡平台給予學生功課，而家長亦需要在家督促子女溫習和交功課。同樣需要停課的中國大陸，最近工信部就推出「國家中小學網絡雲課堂」部署。<br />\n<br />\n工信部要求中國電信、中國移動、中國聯通、阿里巴巴、百度、華為等企業建立專項工作組，確保中小學網絡課堂能夠穩定運行，而工信部則會加強保障中小學生在疫情期間，網上學習的網絡能夠暢通無阻。大陸傳媒報道指各地網絡基礎條件存在差異，加上全國學生一同開始上網學習，容易出現網絡擠塞，所以要加強網絡運行保障。<br />\n<br />\n來源：cnbeta<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/17/china-student-learn-online-during-wars-outbreak/life-tech/love-your-child/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F17%2Fchina-student-learn-online-during-wars-outbreak%2Flife-tech%2Flove-your-child%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=a61be40d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/17/china-student-learn-online-during-wars-outbreak/life-tech/love-your-child/</a><br />\n<br />\n實況：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avjg94r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Favjg94r.png&h=9124d8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubAwev6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubAwev6.png&h=a34a9d85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXKEops.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXKEops.png&h=2d12958f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNudsQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNudsQ8.jpg&h=f6408f65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zk0j7Ra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzk0j7Ra.jpg&h=e84410d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72